{
  "stem": "25651.13",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He doesn't come into the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He wants me to come to the wire.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And because it was getting dark and we were being dismissed, I sort of made as if I didn't see him, and I disappeared, because I didn't want any favors from him at this juncture.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Who knows what he wanted to-- what he would've thought of me asking for a job in Gross-Rosen when we were destined to leave anyway?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, I didn't know that we were leaving, but we did leave.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now we were put into cattle trucks again, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and it was now really cold, and people died quite, quite badly.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were throwing them out of the truck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the truck got emptier.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was more and more room as the journey proceeded.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Germans would put us in a siding, wait all day, and then we would go through the night.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was all done, you know, so that the population shouldn't see us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we didn't know where we were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We kept-- here and there, you would see someone, so we would ask where we are.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they would tell us a name, and you wouldn't know where it was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't recall.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't-- I didn't know the geography of Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew some of the names of towns, but I didn't know where the towns were.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And the other prisoners were throwing these bodies out that died.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I didn't even tell you about the rollwagen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Dead bodies are, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] are very difficult to handle, because when you lift it in one place, it falls down in another place.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
